 ### Fixed
 
+* Fix indentation of class body when class has multiline super type list (ktlint_official only). Classes with primary constructor parameters (implicit constructor) no longer have their class body incorrectly indented when they have multiline super type lists. Classes with explicit constructor keyword continue to have proper indentation for both constructor and super type lists. `indent`
